title: Personal Portfolio Website
description: A personal portfolio website to showcase my projects and skills. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create a responsive and visually appealing design.

title: Recipe Analysis
description: A web application that analyzes recipes for nutritional content. Users can input their favorite recipes and receive detailed information about calories, macronutrients, and dietary suitability.

title: Deceptive Visualization Project
description: A project focused on creating visualizations that intentionally mislead or deceive the viewer. The aim is to raise awareness about the ethical implications of data visualization and the importance of accurate representation.
